@startuml 1C_User_Login
title 1-C · User Login & Token Issuance (UC-P01, UC-P02, UC-T01, UC-F02)

start
|User|
:Open the correct login page\n(Platform Admin / Tenant Admin / Fan);
:Enter email and password;

|System|
:Identify authentication context;
:Validate credentials and account status;
if (Credentials valid?) then (No)
  :Return 401 authentication error;
  stop
else (Yes)
  if (Tenant-scoped login?) then (Yes)
    :Resolve tenant and check status;
    if (Tenant ACTIVE?) then (No)
      :Return 403 tenant unavailable;
      stop
    else (Yes)
      :Continue authentication;
    endif
  else (No)
    :Continue platform admin login;
  endif
endif

if (Platform Admin with MFA enabled?) then (Yes)
  :Issue partial token\nmfa_required = true;
  |Service Admin|
  :Enter 6-digit TOTP token;
  |System|
  :Verify MFA token;
  if (MFA token valid?) then (No)
    :Return 422 and require retry;
    stop
  else (Yes)
    :Issue full bearer token;
  endif
else (No)
  :Issue bearer token;
endif

|System|
:Attach role, tenant scope and permissions to token;
:Update last_login_at;

if (Resolved role?) then (Service Admin)
  |Service Admin|
  :Open Platform Admin dashboard;
elseif (Resolved role?) then (Tenant Admin)
  |Tenant Admin|
  :Open Tenant Admin dashboard;
else (Registered Fan)
  |Registered Fan|
  :Return to fansite as logged-in fan;
endif

stop
@enduml
